styles.name: Medium
styles.sampletext: Uncle has devoted his life in retirement to two things: long term chairs, and passing financial literacy to the masses via catchy, innovative rhyme-schemes paired with contemporary hip hop beats. Some would argue that Uncle is a pioneer, fathering (or Uncle-ing) his own sub genre that resonates deeply with Wall Street professionals and hip hop heads alike. Uncle often speaks of positivity, respect, blessings and a profound love for God. When confronted with adversity that challenges his deep-rooted foundation of positivity, Uncle has one answer: ima do it anywayyy!
